        1.万物已近极致<br/>
        Everything is at its acme<br/>
        2.品性与智慧<br/>
        Character and intellect<br/>
        3.做事时常留有悬念<br/>
        Keep matters for a time in suspense<br/>
        4.有识亦应有胆<br/>
        Knowledge and courage<br/>
        5.让别人依赖你<br/>
        Create a feeling of dependence<br/>
        6.至善至美的境界<br/>
        A man at his highest point<br/>
        7.不要比上司更耀眼<br/>
        Avoid victories over superiors<br/>
        8.不被激情左右<br/>
        To be without passions<br/>
        9.避免土生土长的缺陷<br/>
        Avoid the faults of your nation<br/>
        10.财富与名望<br/>
        Fortune and fame<br/>
        11.择师而交<br/>
        Cultivate those who can teach you<br/>
